29:31.518 --> 29:52.870
headquarters in Salzburg, to see the G2 as a 
personnel officer, two-star general. I went down

29:52.890 --> 29:54.072
there, I'm going home. I'm going to get out of this 
man's army and go make some money. And he said, I

