don't have anything on you, kid. You got a job. Just 
keep on doing like you are. And he gave me that for a

30:04.746 --> 30:06.187
month. And I kept making a nuisance of myself, 
thinking that the squeaky wheel would get the

30:07.208 --> 30:11.432
grease. And I passed him in the hall one day. And he 
said, come in here, kid. Well, I saw something on

30:16.396 --> 30:17.978
you yesterday. And he looked through his desk, 
worst looking mind, and gave it to me. Here it is.

30:24.644 --> 30:25.825
You're going to Vienna tomorrow. I said, oh, 
General, there's something wrong. There's a

30:31.284 --> 30:32.866
misunderstanding here somewhere. He looked over 
his eyes and glanced at me and said, yeah, kid,

30:33.687 --> 30:40.094
well, you have something that's wrong. You're 
going to Vienna tomorrow. You're not going home.

30:44.179 --> 30:57.094
