31:59.680 --> 32:01.102
go. And I thoroughly enjoyed it. It was well worth 
the seven, eight months I was down there. Because

32:11.418 --> 32:15.964
Austria is a beautiful country, and I've made a lot 
of good acquaintances there. I saw some gorgeous

32:16.064 --> 32:18.889
country, and I accomplished something. We got the 
power plants running to some degree. We got juice

32:23.896 --> 32:29.164
back into the major cities and some of the little 
country towns. So I felt that I accomplished

32:29.836 --> 32:32.120
something. So I don't regret it. It just took six, 
seven, eight months more of my life away and I'm

32:34.744 --> 32:42.236
nothing worse for it I guess. Okay, then after that 
you went up to the company commander or the CO of the

