43:57.706 --> 44:09.477
setting our goals to be combat proficient. 
meaning that each battalion had to pass the

44:10.672 --> 44:32.478
basic battalion test, combat proficiency test, 
that every unit that went to combat overseas had to

44:10.672 --> 44:32.478
pass before they were certified combat 
proficient.

44:34.660 --> 44:37.183
Isn't that quite a demand to make on reservists? 
